{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/887720/extras/Combat.gif?t=1721723222\" /><br><br>Based on the original novel by Pawe\u0142 Le\u015bniak, \u201cEquilibrium\u201d, this third-person action game resurrects the everlasting fight between light and darkness, as a full-fledged war between Angels and Demons seems imminent and our world is the proposed battleground. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/887720/extras/banner_story.jpg?t=1721723222\" /><br><br>You play as Desmond, once a bon vivant son of a rich entrepreneur. Desmond\u2019s life has been drawn into a sequence of unfortunate events that have led him to lose most of his humanity. Making a deal with the devil, Desmond gains demonic powers, becoming the hell\u2019s executor. He is both the destroyer and the savior, with his human part gradually deteriorating as his hunger for vengeance grows. He fights fiercely with his fists and claws, making use of the skills offered by his demonic and human side. Passing through the gates of hell and back, he will eventually have to decide about his impact on the future of humanity.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/887720/extras/banner_features.jpg?t=1721723222\" /><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Fast-paced combat </strong>- Punch, slash, and kick your way through the armies of demons and angels in Devil\u2019s Hunt hack \u2018n slash battles. <br></li><li><strong>Change forms</strong> \u2013 Unleash your inner demon by flipping between Desmond\u2018s human and infernal form. Choose between 3 different fighting schools to conquer each challenge your way!<br></li><li><strong>Story based on \u2018Equilibrium\u2019</strong> \u2013 Devil\u2019s Hunt is based on the Polish novel series and its story is told through cinematic cutscenes.<br></li><li><strong>Explore the depths of hell</strong> - Devil\u2019s Hunt takes Desmond to many locations, including hell itself. Venture into rich environments like Miami, and Jerusalem.</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/887720/extras/Special.gif?t=1721723222\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Desmond","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/887720/db21d24282db567d4880ab7bd48153f1bbc29749.jpg"},{"name":"Savior","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/887720/380ef5b00e5420daebcdefcce6ba77e835cbf226.jpg"},{"name":"Destroyer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/887720/af0121d1d070ef82052d9b909160c085d7954e1f.jpg"},{"name":"Soul collector","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/887720/f83fddb5fe53ea0cd8506277952c8886404adc2f.jpg"},{"name":"Awaken!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/887720/e071de6cb16fe02b57a75f5786fda9b73afd8cb1.jpg"},{"name":"Death is only the beginning","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/887720/02387646d6cfdeea3a9800339e907d38726b7887.jpg"},{"name":"I want to break free!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/887720/7eeee4ebb75e09d9a94fadc7cb67f119c4406b3c.jpg"},{"name":"Why does it have to be snake?","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/887720/abf8bdf7a5f4756ef14ec9beb12ba1810a5cf72e.jpg"},{"name":"Angel's fall","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/887720/637fed0845e244f13563aa80235c3a532b16eb16.jpg"},{"name":"A false friend","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/887720/c251255a253e1b5a4d3e7f4dfeb0b25eae067ba7.jpg"}],"total":30},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/ste